(Arduino GND)

Wire going from Arduino GND → breadboard blue (–) rail

Ultrasonic Sensor (HC-SR04)

Wire going from Arduino 5V → breadboard red (+) rail

Wire going from breadboard red (+) rail → breadboard hole A10

Ultrasonic VCC pin → breadboard hole A10

Wire going from Arduino pin 9 → breadboard hole A11

Ultrasonic TRIG pin → breadboard hole A11

Wire going from Arduino pin 10 → breadboard hole A12

Ultrasonic ECHO pin → breadboard hole A12

Ultrasonic GND pin → breadboard hole A13

Wire going from breadboard hole A13 → breadboard blue (–) rail

Servo Motor (Parking Barrier)

Servo signal wire (yellow/white) → breadboard hole A20

Wire going from breadboard hole A20 → Arduino pin 6

Servo ground wire (brown/black) → breadboard blue (–) rail

Servo power wire (red) → external battery pack positive (+)

External Battery Pack

Battery pack negative (–) → breadboard blue (–) rail
